headline: NextEra Energy to meet with investors at the end of May and throughout June
summary: NextEra Energy, Inc. (NYSE: NEE) today announced that members of the senior management team will participate in various investor meetings at the end of May and throughout June to discuss, among other things, long-term growth-rate expectations. Investors and other interested parties can access a copy of the most recent presentation materials at www.NextEraEnergy.com/investors.
